data.description: This well sought out Steamboat model is located in a private cul-de-sac in the 55 + community of Anthem Ranch. Home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths along with a den. Hardwood floors throughout with a beautiful built in cabinet in the spacious living room area. Kitchen with center granite island and stainless steel appliances. Large master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and 5 piece master bath. Gorgeous trex covered patio with fenced in yard to enjoy the beautiful Colorado sunsets. Easy access to Boulder, Denver and DIA. Active community with so much to do. Miles of trails, hundreds of clubs to enjoy and beautiful views. Add your personal touches to make this home your own.
